Template: elkarbackup/dbadminname
Type: string
Description: User name of Mysql admin:
 It will be used to create the initial database, user and password.

Template: elkarbackup/dbadminpassword
Type: password
Description: Password of Mysql admin:
 It will be used to create the initial database, user and password.

Template: elkarbackup/dbhost
Type: string
Default: localhost
Description: DB host:
 The application will connect to the database in this host.

Template: elkarbackup/dbname
Type: string
Default: elkarbackup
Description: DB name:
 The application will connect to this database.

Template: elkarbackup/dbusername
Type: string
Default: elkarbackup
Description: DB user:
 The application will connect to the database using this user.

Template: elkarbackup/dbuserpassword
Type: password
Default: elkarbackup
Description: DB user password:
 The application will connect to the database using this password.
